items.name: social-events-detector
items.description: Social Events Detector is a free software whose main functionality is social event detection. The software allows you to analyse the metadata of a picture and classify it in nine different possibilities: concert, conference, exhibition, fashion, protest, sports, theatre dance, others or non-event. This software is useful for people who works with lots of metadata and picture and he want to order the big quantity of data by themes.
